<L>__{exterior canyon trail dusk}
<A>__{troops are moving through the trees quietly, sabers drawn.}
<L>__{exterior canyon rim dusk}
<A>__{the rest of the troops have moved to the edge. they too are quiet. down below, the pawnee scouts are milling about looking for sign. the soldiers from the canyon floor are silently arriving on the scene. the pawnee look to the lead scout on the canyon rim. they have no answer, and the lead scout has none to give the general at his side. ten bears' village is gone.}
